    testthat,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
VignetteBuilder: knitr
biocViews: GeneExpression,
    DifferentialExpression,
    GeneSetEnrichment,
    DimensionReduction,
    Pathways
